room_title: Escape room "Conspiracy" by Clue IQ in Frederick
room_address: 103 S. Carroll St, Suite 1A, Frederick, MD 21701
room_description: With less than an hour to uncover the grisly details before mysterious agents arrive on scene, the players must piece together clues and connect the dots to solve the biggest mystery of their lives. Sharpen your investigative skills, grab your tin foil hats, and see if you can unravel the conspiracy.
